These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
City: prague, new-york, marseilles, liverpool, london
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
The people have 5 different jobs:  firefighter, photographer, freelancer, writer, paramedic
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the firefighter is on the left of the freelancer##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person traveling to london is between the photographer and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the writer is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the paramedic is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| City      | prague        | new-york | london     | marseilles   | liverpool |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Job   | writer  | photographer     | firefighter | freelancer | paramedic  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

