.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
5 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, chess, domino, billiard
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, golf, water-polo, swimming, basketball
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is between the chinese and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the indian is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the indian is the person playing chess##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Game         | domino | backgammon | billiard    | monopoly  | chess    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Sport     | water-polo    | golf | basketball | swimming | baseball |

