.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
House: farmhouse, ranch-style, modern, victorian, craftsman
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, bus, scooter, bike, boat
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
 4. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the farmhouse house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the victorian house##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the craftsman house and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| House   | craftsman  | ranch-style | farmhouse | victorian | modern        |
