 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person playing backgammon and the person watching family movies##2
 5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person playing domino##1
 9. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
10. the person playing backgammon is the british##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
12. the british is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
13. the person playing domino is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
