.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, purple, light-blue, pink
There 5 different types of food: apricot, broccoli, lettuce, orange, watermelon
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer, manager, social-worker, writer
House: gothic-revival, cottage, ranch-style, cape-cod, craftsman
 1. the cottage house is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 4. the person who likes purple is between the cottage house and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes green is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Color   | light-blue       | pink       | red   | purple      | green    |
| Food       | watermelon | orange        | apricot       | lettuce       | broccoli |
| Job        | writer     | lawyer        | social-worker | dancer        | manager  |
| House      | cape-cod | ranch-style | gothic-revival      | craftsman | cottage  |

