.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, siglo, bluemaster, davidoff
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, blood-red, lilac, turquise, fuchsia
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, rowing, skiing, volleyball
 1. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the davidoff-smoker and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
 9. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the bluemaster-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
13. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | water      | sprite   | fanta   | soy-milk   |
| Cigar   | davidoff    | bluemaster   | siglo   | blend | montecristo     |
