.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, november, may, march, july
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, gospel, dubstep, salsa, techno
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train, trike, van
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is the fan of salsa##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person who's sport is golf and the fan of dubstep##2
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fan of techno##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Birthday    | may       | march    | july | november  | august        |
| Music-Genre       | techno | house | dubstep  | salsa | gospel    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, card-games, filmmaking, reading, traveling
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
House: colonial, ranch-style, cape-cod, victorian, wooden
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person watching crime movies and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is the fisherman##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the victorian house##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the pilot and the ranch-style house##2
 7. the victorian house is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is the cape-cod house##1
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Hobby      | baking      | card-games         | reading      | filmmaking | traveling     |
| Job           | engineer | entrepreneur | fisherman | pilot    | bartender  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| House   | cape-cod  | ranch-style        | colonial   | victorian    | wooden     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: victoriand-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, october, september, april, december
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
House: cottage, victorian, townhouse, palace, art-deco
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the victorian house##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 4. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's birthday is in february and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the cottage house and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is victoriand-games##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's hobby is victoriand-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is victoriand-games is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | victoriand-games |
| Birthday   | february   | april    | october | december | september      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| House     | townhouse | art-deco        | cottage  | victorian        | palace    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, snooker, goldfish-climbing, canasta
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goat, bird, horse, goldfish
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the malaysian and the owner of the goldfish##2
 3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the thai and the owner of the bird##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the horse##1
 8. the person playing goldfish-climbing is the owner of the goat##1
 9. the american is the owner of the goat##1
10. the person playing goldfish-climbing is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Game         | snooker    | canasta  | monopoly  | backgammon      | goldfish-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Pet   | bird | guinea-pig    | goldfish    | horse       | goat         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 